NNAAMMEE
       ddeebbuugg - Debug module with node-inspector

SSYYNNOOPPSSIISS
       slc debug [options] [module]

OOPPTTIIOONNSS
       --hh, ----hheellpp
              print usage information

       --cc, ----ccllii
              prevent auto opening web browser

       --pp, ----ppoorrtt <<ppoorrtt>>
              start debugger on port

       --ss, ----ssuussppeenndd
              suspend on first line

       --dd, ----ddeebbuugg--ppoorrtt <<ppoorrtt>>
              use an alternate debug port

       mmoodduullee module to debug.

       Use .. to debug the application in the current directory.

       If no module is specified, then slc will start REPL and load the module
       in the current directory.

